102 dalmatians is a 1996 american animated musical comedy film directed by don bluth and written by dodie smith . the film is a sequel to the 2000 film the dalmatians . the film was released in the united states on august 23 , 1996 . the film was released on august 23 , 1996 , by buena vista distribution . the film was released on dvd in the united states on august 12 , 1996 .